{
  "2133760": {
    "name": "小小书店",
    "steam_appid": 2133760,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你是否也曾想过，抛下一切，把书店开到风景如画的海边？ </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《小小书店》中，这不再是一个梦想。没有打卡，没有KPI和OKR，只有海风、书香和你精心打理的移动书店。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/87a4c2f4a804089caef5cc3441abe592.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=618 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/87a4c2f4a804089caef5cc3441abe592.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/87a4c2f4a804089caef5cc3441abe592.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/ca225ac2a9a4acf90dc52b8e9c71daf0.avif?t=1769192503\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >告别固定的店面，这次你的书店长了轮子！在悠闲的海边小镇，亲手打理这家独特的房车书店。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不仅仅是好看：</strong> 自由布置绿植、烛台和家具。装饰风格不只影响视觉氛围，更会直接改变光顾的顾客类型与书籍销量。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造经营流派：</strong> 逐步解锁更多内容，塑造属于你独一无二的经营成长路线。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/6ad886a66de14f8d3b0715273733b44f.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/6ad886a66de14f8d3b0715273733b44f.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/6ad886a66de14f8d3b0715273733b44f.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/16081011d229aab72ca804229202d48b.avif?t=1769192503\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >观察顾客的兴趣，从成千上万种组合中进货。合理的选书与推荐将提升销售表现，也会推动剧情的发展。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深度本地化书目：</strong> 游戏内书目基于真实出版物库，并专为中文版本进行了特别本地化适配。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>邂逅熟悉作品：</strong> 我们精心收录了大量来自中文出版领域的作品，让你在虚拟书店中也能读到熟悉又意外的作品。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/5575d68f77b729534bde289f99a02353.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/5575d68f77b729534bde289f99a02353.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/5575d68f77b729534bde289f99a02353.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/222c7c0a86aebdc3423d6f76fc314f3a.avif?t=1769192503\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  书山镇的居民温暖友好，却也个个性格鲜明，带着各自的小秘密。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>解锁个人剧情：</strong> 通过交谈、帮助与日常互动，逐渐敲开他们的心扉。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>书写小镇故事：</strong> 一点一滴拼凑出这座海边小镇背后的回忆、情感与人际羁绊。 </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/166839d190ce991d91022f87f18fa865.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=600 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/166839d190ce991d91022f87f18fa865.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/166839d190ce991d91022f87f18fa865.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/4f7098254b60b81be4b7e313bc59e5d8.avif?t=1769192503\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >书山镇不仅只有书店。发动引擎，在街巷间漫步，参与季节节庆，发现隐藏的风景。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/57c78bd2986cc7ab805c8ddee2315e5a.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/57c78bd2986cc7ab805c8ddee2315e5a.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/57c78bd2986cc7ab805c8ddee2315e5a.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>集邮册玩法：</strong> 你的每一次探索和互动，都有机会获得独特的<strong>纪念邮票</strong>。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充满惊喜的旅程：</strong> 填满你的邮票册，每一枚邮票都记录着一段回忆，解锁更多隐藏事件，让你的“慢生活”始终充满目标感。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/c53b9d73ccd472a51349cacf6a54820b.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/c53b9d73ccd472a51349cacf6a54820b.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/c53b9d73ccd472a51349cacf6a54820b.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/72a45d721b439426d7a2cfd7ba0185b8.avif?t=1769192503\" width=780 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>充实的内容：</strong> 游戏提供约 <strong>25–30 小时</strong> 的主线体验，并包含大量可选支线内容与成就挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游玩建议：</strong> 适合放慢节奏、分多次游玩，在睡前或闲暇时，慢慢感受这段温暖的海边故事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/89c3cb83373c1260c2969871949834d8.poster.avif?t=1769192503\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/89c3cb83373c1260c2969871949834d8.webm?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2133760/extras/89c3cb83373c1260c2969871949834d8.mp4?t=1769192503\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
